# Day 7 — Final Revision

Review only **high-frequency topics**.

Focus on:

* IAM roles
* VPC networking
* gcloud commands
* Storage classes
* Deployment methods

Memorize these CLI commands:

```
gcloud compute instances create
gcloud container clusters create
gcloud storage buckets create
gcloud sql instances create
```

Take **one final practice test**.

